.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003eIf you're building something technical, you already know how to speak the language of precision. This session is about learning when and how to shift toward accessibility and connection so that the people on the other side of the table understand, believe, and say yes.\\r\\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\",\"quote\":\"_\",\"zoom\":\"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/84466942706?pwd=RZdARAXwCH00FJBvFVOillOf0lmty0.1\",\"city\":\"San Francisco\",\"address\":\"Cooley LLP, 3 Embarcadero Ctr 20th Floor, San Francisco, CA 94111\",\"timezone\":\"America/Los_Angeles\",\"end_time\":\"2026-06-25 19:00:00\",\"start_time\":\"2026-06-25 16:00:00\",\"emt_event_id\":null,\"finished_at\":null,\"auto_invited\":true,\"image\":\"events/nTvtDI6xRklcQ4ytRbPbmdCz3i7hRgH4wxTIZnew.png\",\"tenant_id\":\"seattle1\",\"speaker_id\":53,\"template\":\"regular\",\"template_info\":[],\"is_pinned\":false,\"include_staff\":false,\"speaker\":{\"id\":53,\"tenant_id\":\"seattle1\",\"name\":\"Tre Balchowsky\",\"email\":\"tre@trebalchowsky.com\",\"is_expert\":false,\"linkedin\":\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/trebalchowsky/\",\"website\":\"Balchowsky Consulting\",\"description\":\"Tre Balchowsky is a public speaking and storytelling coach who works with founders and executives to help them translate complex ideas and technology into stories that move people to action.\u0026nbsp;\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003eShe has coached clients through talks for TED and AWS re:Invent, high-stakes investor pitches, and the kind of early customer events that determine whether a company finds traction or stalls out. Her clients have closed significant funding rounds, built loyal audiences, and landed the talent they needed to grow, often by learning what a story actually is and how to tell one with confidence.\u0026nbsp;\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003eWith a